{"tid":919172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女借貓一去無回頭","createTime":"2018-11-28T00:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T04:22:10.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"28d03f725542917eba3c0871bc8111c8150ba6f7","tid":919172,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181127&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58965527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181127%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58965527&d=XvVZL%2BGN6co3a6t8aNcdLU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d45c4695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181127%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58965527&h=b246905f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181127&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58965527</a> <br />\n貓店長「皮蛋」太可愛 少女「借走」一去無回頭<br />\n<br />\n旺角發生懷疑偷貓事件。本月5日晚上，一名年約20歲的<span style=\"color: red;\">少女走到花園街櫻桃麵包西餅店，逗玩店外一隻叫「皮蛋」的貓店長，其間向店員提出借貓的要求，應承兩日後歸還</span>，店員見她非常有誠意，答應將皮蛋借出，詎料皮蛋一借無回頭。店員其後製作尋貓啟事張貼店外，盼街坊助尋皮蛋，並呼籲拍照上載fb廣傳。直至今日下午5時許，店員見借貓女仍未現身，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場後，翻查閉路電視錄影，終尋獲借貓的少女，據悉她承諾一兩日內會將皮蛋歸還，店員亦接受，警方列作雜項處理。"},{"pid":"856fbe1d690e0faad4a140a007e42b6c5d6c0cce","tid":919172,"uid":176303,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:22:18.000Z","msg":"真心想知咩原因先會令個奴隸店員去借主人出去比其他街邊奴隸?"},{"pid":"f9d26054eb391dcb37df6b8fee5c5322c6d62830","tid":919172,"uid":82532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"借嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaddf5ed3f42c5edb4c2db018b347ab2881e905","tid":919172,"uid":66943,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:30:32.000Z","msg":"馬總統看錶"},{"pid":"2a1ecd5d3576ab287692fa0672ab9a6ee78cc925","tid":919172,"uid":198583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T00:39:05.00