ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母緊係婉拒個客，之後過兩日貓店長係門口曬太陽時比條仆街巴士狗偷撚走左<br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母都唔知，以為佢上左倉訓覺，後來搵唔到又有街坊話見佢比人抱走左<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，正賤種黎，想養走去偷人隻貓<br />\n街坊又唔撚早出聲/阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老豆老母事後又唔報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大個諗番嬲撚到"},{"pid":"2068df26525ae8dae4bcfa0be73f30cd2005464a","tid":919172,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T04:12:31.000Z","msg":"借嘢唔還點解係雜項而唔為偷竊？"}]}